Component Rules:

Each component must be reusable.

Keep components small.

Example:

ProposalCard only displays proposal data.

VoteButtons handles vote actions.

Services handle blockchain calls.

Hooks manage data fetching and contract events.

Reactivity:

Frontend should listen for smart contract events:

ProposalCreated
VoteCast
FundingReceived

When events fire:

Update proposals list
Update vote counts
Update funding progress
Update activity feed

UI style rules:

Flat design
1px borders
Simple spacing
No animations
No gradients
Dark background
White text
Green accent

Responsive design:

Mobile friendly
Stacked layout on small screens

Goal result:

A clean, minimal Web3 DAO dashboard that clearly demonstrates reactive blockchain governance interactions.
